text: Félix Alegría (born 20 November 1876, date of death unknown) was a Chilean sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Chilean male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Chile Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Linares Province
